    "summary": "The user describes post-surgical symptoms (redness, warmth, and yellow discharge) following a cyst removal and asks if they can self-treat with warm compresses and antibiotic cream. The assistant initially dismisses the signs of infection as normal healing and encourages self-treatment, but later pivots to recommending a doctor's visit when pressed by the user.",
